high_descs: Go forward and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the potato out and shut the door of the fridge.
Go left and then turn to the right to face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the potato out again.
Go right and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the potato in and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge on your left.
Grab a potato from the fridge.
Go to the microwave on your left.
Put the potato in the microwave, then take it out.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and cool it.

high_descs: Go to the other side of the room and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Take the potato out of the fridge.
Go to the counter to the left of the fridge where the microwave is.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the potato when it is done cooking.
Go to the right to the fridge.
Put the cooked potato inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato inside the fridge.
